 The number of fatalities in the bus that overturned in Graskop on the R532 on Sunday has climbed to nine, according to communication officer ofÂ  community safety, security and liaison, Moeti Mmusi. The accident occurred between Graskop and Ohrigstad yesterday. Seven of the 46 passengers, all male, were confirmed to have died yesterday. ALSO READ: Seven dead after bus overturns on the R532 between Graskop and Orighstad The 39 survivors were treated at Matibidi and Kiaat Private hospitals, where two more passengers passed away. Investigations into the crash are continuing and Mmusi was not able to verify whether the driver numbered among the deceased.